## 📊 Skill-Gap Analysis & Market Demand Insights

### 1. Market Demand Insights
* **High Demand Skills:** Native Android Development (Kotlin/Compose), Robust Backend Architecture (Node.js, Express), State Management, and API Integration.
* **Industry Trends:** Companies are heavily looking for developers who understand both frontend UI design patterns and efficient database scaling.

### 2. Identified Skill Gaps
* **Technical Gaps:** Need to deepen understanding of Advanced Data Structures (DSA) for optimization and advanced system design concepts.
* **Tools/Libraries:** Working with automated testing frameworks and cloud deployment (like AWS/Heroku) for backend services.

